s%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fquad-is-here-to-stay-says-pm-modi-as-india-prepares-to-host-2025-summit%2Farticleshow%2F113559200.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20PM%20Modi%20And%20Joe%20Biden%20Hold%20Bilateral%20Talks%2C%20A%20Mega%20Drone%20Deal%20Firms%20Up%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20the%20United%20States%20today%20firmed%20up%20multi-billion%20dollar%20drone%20deal%20as%20PM%20Modi%20met%20Joe%20Biden%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20his%20three-day%20visit%20to%20the%20US.%20PM%20Modi%20held%20bilateral%20talks%20with%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20the%20two%20leaders%20discussed%20a%20range%20of%20issues%20to%20further%20strengthen%20India-US%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drone%20deal%20was%20also%20discussed%20in%20detail%20by%20both%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20procuring%2031%20MQ-9B%20Sky%20Guardian%20and%20Sea%20Guardian%20drones%20from%20the%20United%20States.%20The%20cost%20to%20acquire%20these%20drones%20is%20nearly%20%243%20billion.%20India%20aims%20to%20heighten%20the%20surveillance%20apparatus%20of%20the%20armed%20forces%2C%20especially%20along%20the%20frontier%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20talks%20for%20this%20deal%20have%20been%20on%20for%20well%20over%20a%20year%20now.%20In%20June%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Defence%20Ministry%20approved%20the%20procurement%20of%20the%20MQ-9B%20Sky%20Guardian%20and%20Sea%20Guardian%20armed%20drones%20with%20air-to-surface%20missiles%20and%20laser-guided%20bombs%20from%20the%20US%20under%20a%20government-to-government%20framework.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20purchasing%20the%20drones%2C%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20is%20also%20looking%20to%20conclude%20two%20other%20major%20defence%20deals%20this%20financial%20year%20-%203%20more%20Scorpene%20submarines%20and%2026%20Rafale-M%20fighter%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETHE%20MQ-9B%20SKY%20GUARDIAN%20AND%20SEA%20GUARDIAN%20DRONES%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MQ-9B%20drone%20is%20a%20high-altitude%20long-endurance%20remotely-piloted%20unmanned%20aircraft%20manufactures%20and%20sold%20by%20US%20defence%20firm%20General%20Atomics.%20It%20is%20known%20for%20delivering%20persistent%20intelligence%2C%20surveillance%2C%20and%20reconnaissance%20(ISR).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20designed%20to%20fly%20over%20the%20horizon%20via%20satellite%20for%20up%20to%2040%2B%20hours%20in%20all%20types%20of%20weather%20and%20safely%20integrate%20into%20civil%20airspace%2C%20enabling%20joint%20forces%20and%20civil%20authorities%20to%20deliver%20real-time%20situational%20awareness%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%94day%20or%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20General%20Atomics%2C%20the%20drone%20can%20be%20configured%20to%20conduct%20a%20number%20of%20ISR%20operations%2C%20including%20but%20not%20limited%20to%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHumanitarian%20Assistance%2FDisaster%20Relief%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESearch%20and%20Rescue%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMaritime%20domain%20awareness%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAnti-surface%20warfare%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAnti-submarine%20warfare%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAirborne%20mine%20countermeasures%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAirborne%20early%20warning%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EElectronic%20warfare%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELong-range%20strategic%20ISR%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOver-the-horizon%20targeting%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Predator%20drone%20has%20an%20impressive%20and%20proven%20record%20in%20West%20Asia%20as%20well%20as%20in%20Afghanistan.%20It%20is%20valued%20for%20its%20precision%20bombing%20capabilities%20and%20eliminating%20high-value%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Predator%20drone%20is%20a%20variant%20of%20the%20MQ-9%20%26quot%3BReaper%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20was%20used%20to%20launch%20a%20modified%20version%20of%20the%20Hellfire%20missile%20that%20killed%20Al%20Qaeda%20leader%20Ayman%20al-Zawahiri%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Kabul%20in%20July%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EINDIAN%20ARMED%20FORCES%20-%20WHO%20GETS%20WHAT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2031%20drones%20that%20will%20be%20purchased%20from%20General%20Atomics%20will%20be%20divided%20between%20the%20Indian%20Navy%2C%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20and%20Indian%20Army.%2016%20of%20the%20MQ-9B%20drones%20will%20be%20allocated%20to%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20to%20increase%20its%20surveillance%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20region%2C%20eight%20will%20be%20given%20to%20the%20Indian%20Army%20for%20use%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20with%20China%20and%20Line%20of%20Control%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20the%20remaining%20eight%20will%20be%20assigned%20to%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20for%20precision%2C%20targeted%20missions%20across%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drone%20deal%20must%20be%20agreed%20upon%20and%20signed%20by%20both%20India%20and%20the%20United%20States%20before%20October%2031%2C%202024%2C%20after%20which%20the%20approximately%20%243%20billion%20price%20will%20be%20up%20for%20revision%20on%20part%20of%20the%20manufacturer%20-%20General%20Atomics%2C%20as%20per%20talks%20between%20both%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20and%20his%20delegation%20was%20given%20a%20detailed%20brief%20on%20the%20capability%20and%20other%20specifics%20of%20the%20drone%20during%20his%20official%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PM%20Modi%20visiting%20the%20US%2C%20both%20nations%20will%20prioritise%20the%20deal%20and%20want%20to%20make%20progress%20before%20the%20October%2031%20date%20lapses.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726955940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fp00a3994_mq-9b-sky-guardian-drone-general-atomics_625x300_22_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-modi-us-visit-as-pm-narendra-modi-and-joe-biden-hold-bilateral-talks-