20basis%20of%20her%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDefendant%20Lauren%20S%C3%A1nchez%2C%20who%20had%20previously%20expressed%20oral%20and%20written%20interest%20in%20collaborating%20with%20Plaintiff%2C%20subsequently%20used%20Plaintiff's%20book%20concept%20without%20Plaintiff's%20consent%20or%20authorization%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d1fe7fa0-2a34-47e8-a6ee-7cf033770723%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EZabel%20is%20also%20suing%20S%C3%A1nchez%20for%20intentionally%20inflicting%20emotional%20distress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20said%20Zabel%20is%20a%20private%20yoga%20instructor%20in%20California%20who%20worked%20with%20S%C3%A1nchez%20from%202007%20to%202010.%20Zabel%20has%20authored%20children's%20books%20that%20are%20available%20for%20purchase%20on%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20women%20engaged%20in%20verbal%20and%20written%20discussions%20%26quot%3Bspanning%2016%20years%26quot%3B%20about%20a%20%26quot%3Bpotential%20partnership%20to%20write%20a%20children's%20book%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202022%2C%20Plaintiff%20reached%20out%20directly%20to%20Defendant%20via%20email%2C%20text%2C%20and%20Instagram%2C%20sharing%20a%20specific%20book%20concept%20with%20Defendant%2C%20about%20a%20cat%20who%20flies%20to%20Mars%2C%20re-opening%20prior%20discussions%20(from%202007-2010)%2C%20and%20trusting%20her%20with%20the%20intellectual%20property%20and%20concept%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20said%20the%20email%20also%20revitalized%20conversations%20about%20a%20partnership%20between%20the%20two%2C%20including%20promoting%20Zabel's%20children's%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BDharma%20Kitty%20Goes%20to%20Mars%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20would%20involve%20giving%20the%20proceeds%20to%20Bezos%20Earth%20Fund%20and%20Bezos%20Academy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20said%20Zabel%20published%20%26quot%3BDharma%20Kitty%20Goes%20to%20Mars%26quot