n%20the%20two%20leaders%20as%20both%20had%20risen%20from%20humble%20beginnings%20to%20the%20highest%20offices%20in%20their%20respective%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20first%20visit%20to%20the%20country%20after%20becoming%20prime%20minister%20the%20same%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20mother%20lived%20in%20their%20old%20home%20in%20Gujarat%20till%20she%20passed%20away%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20highlighted%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20ability%20to%20connect%20with%20world%20leaders%2C%20including%20US%20presidents%2C%20and%20forge%20deeper%20bonds%2C%20noting%20that%20he%20connects%20with%20them%20at%20a%20personal%20level%2C%20drawing%20on%20his%20own%20life%20experiences%20to%20bridge%20cultural%20and%20geopolitical%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20embarked%20on%20a%20three-day%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20to%20attend%20a%20summit%20of%20the%20Quad%20grouping%20and%20address%20a%20key%20conclave%20at%20the%20United%20Nations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726935540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-06%2Fpm-modi-obama-reuters_650x400_71465292501.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhen-pm-once-told-obama-your-limousine-was-as-big-as-my-mothers-house-6618267%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20told%20Barack%20Obama%20in%202014%20that%20the%20size%20of%20the%20then-US%20president's%20car%20was%20almost%20as%20big%20as%20the%20house%20his%20mother%20lived%20in.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhen-pm-once-told-obama-your-limousine-was-as-big-as-my-mothers-house-6618267%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%201st%20Cancer%20Genome%20Atlas%20Launched%20Ahead%20Of%20Quad's%20'Cancer%20Moonshot'%20Initiative%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20high%20profile%20global%20initiative%20to%20tackle%20cancer%20called%20the%20'Cancer%20Moonshot'%20will%20be%20announced%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20Quad%20Summit.%20Ahead%20of%20that%20an%20India%20cancer%20specific%20cancer%20genome%20atlas%20has%20been%20released.%20Till%20date%2C%20all%20cancer%20treatments%20were%20based%20on%20western%20datasets%2C%20say%20the%20experts%20who%20made%20the%20cancer%20atlas.%20This%20had%20led%20to%20complications.%20India%20has%20the%20third-highest%20number%20of%20cancer%20cases%20after%20the%20US%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20the%20Cancer%20Genome%20Atlas%20of%20India%20is%20timely%20since%20according%20to%20estimates%20by%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%2C%20in%20India%2C%20the%20incidence%20of%20cancer%20cases%20is%20likely%20to%20increase%20from%201.46%20million%20in%202022%20to%201.57%20million%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Quad%20Summit%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Philadelphia%20will%20be%20attended%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20Australian%20Prime%20Minister%20Anthony%20Albanese%20and%20Japanese%20Prime%20Minister%20Fumio%20Kishida.%20While%20global%20security%20will%20be%20high%20on%20the%20agenda%2C%20the%20menace%20of%20cancer%20is%20also%20not%20being%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECancer%20Moonshot%20is%20a%20special%20programme%20spearheaded%20by%20Mr%20Biden%20and%20the%20US%20First%20Lady.%20The%20White%20House%20says%20it%20is%20building%20a%20world%20where%20the%20word%20cancer%20loses%20its%20power%2C%20a%20diagnosis%20isn't%20a%20death%20sentence%2C%20and%20to%20prevent%20cancer%20before%20it%20starts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20catch%20cancer%20early%20so%20people%20live%20longer%20and%20healthier%20lives%2C%20and%20patients%20and%20families%20don't%20have%20to%20navigate%20their%20cancer%20journey%20alone.%20To%20prevent%20more%20than%20four%20million%20cancer%20deaths%20by%202047%20and%20to%20improve%20the%20experience%20of%20people%20who%20are%20touched%20by%20cancer%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Cancer%20Genome%20Atlas%20(ICGA)%20is%20aimed%20at%20transforming%20cancer%20research%20and%20treatment%20for%20the%20Indian%20population.%20Historically%2C%20cancer%20treatments%20in%20India%20have%20been%20based%20on%20western%20data%20sets.%20However%2C%20cancers%20in%20Indian%20patients%20can%20differ%20significantly%20at%20the%20molecular%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICGA's%20mission%20is%20to%20create%20Indian-specific%20datasets%20to%20help%20researchers%20and%20clinicians%20develop%20personalised%20treatment%20protocols.%20This%20new%20open-access%20portal%20represents%20a%20monumental%20step%20in%20revolutionising%20cancer%20research%2C%20specifically%20for%20Indian%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20platform%20consists%20of%20data%20from%2050%20breast%20cancer%20patients%2C%20with%20plans%20to%20expand%20to%20over%20500%20patients%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%20Experts%20suggest%20that%20in%202022%2C%20India%20reported%201.92%20lakh%20cases%20of%20breast%20cancer%2C%20constituting%2026.6%20per%20cent%20of%20all%20cancer%20cases%2C%20along%20with%2098%2C337%20deaths%2C%20accounting%20for%2013.7%20per%20cent%20of%20all%20cancer-related%20fatalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Cancer%20Genome%20Atlas%20(ICGA)%20is%20a%20national%20initiative%20focused%20on%20mapping%20cancers%20across%20India%2C%20supported%20by%20a%20foundation%20formed%20by%20over%2050%20clinicians%2C%20researchers%2C%20and%20data%20analysts.%20Its%20mission%20is%20to%20enhance%20cancer%20diagnosis%20and%20treatment%20for%20Indian%20patients%20and%20contribute%20to%20the%20global%20understanding%20of%20cancer%20biology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20open%20access%20dataset%20will%20drive%20transformative%20breakthroughs%20in%20cancer%20treatment%2C%20said%20professor%20Shekhar%20C%20Mande%2C%20former%20Director%20General%2C%20Council%20of%20Scientific%20and%20Industrial%20Research%20(CSIR)%20and%20currently%20senior%20professor%20at%20Savitribai%20Phule%20Pune%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaking%20this%20invaluable%20cancer%20data%20publicly%20accessible%20marks%20a%20pivotal%20step%20in%20accelerating%20scientific%20discoveries%20and%20enhancing%20patient%20outcomes.%20By%20openly%20sharing%20this%20data%2C%20we%20are%20empowering%20researchers%2C%20clinicians%2C%20and%20innovators%20to%20collaborate%2C%20explore%20new%20frontiers%2C%20and%20drive%20transformative%20breakthroughs%20in%20cancer%20treatment%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mande%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20uniquely%20has%20a%20high%20burden%20of%20cancers%20related%20to%20the%20digestive%20system%3B%20oral%20and%20lung%20cancer%2C%20mostly%20related%20to%20tobacco%20use%3B%20cervical%20cancer%20is%20increasing%20and%20breast%20cancer%20are%20all%20on%20the%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726934700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fd80ofpv_cancer-generic_625x300_23_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findias-1st-cancer-genome-atlas-launched-ahead-of-quads-cancer-moonshot-initiative-6618569%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20high%20profile%20global%20initiative%20to%20tackle%20cancer%20called%20the%20'Cancer%20MoonShot'%20will%20be%20announced%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20Quad%20Summit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findias-1st-cancer-genome-atlas-launched-ahead-of-quads-cancer-moonshot-initiative-6618569%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dissident%20in%20prisoner%20swap%20vows%20to%20return%20to%20Russ