r%20every%20match%2C%20how%20will%20you%20rate%20this%20pitch%2C%26quot%3B%20asked%20out-of-favour%20Bangladesh%20batter%20Tamim%20Iqbal%20on%20JioCinema%20as%20quoted%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Fcricket%2Fravi-shastris-top-reply-as-tamim-iqbal-probes-him-on-pitch-rating-after-17-wickets-fall-on-day-2-9057832.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENews%2018%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTop%20billing%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20cricket%20pitch%2C%26quot%3B%20replied%20Shastri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20it%20has%20something%20for%20every%20bowler.%26quot%3B%20Tamim%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20their%20bowlers%20dismissing%20Bangladesh%20for%20just%20149%20after%20their%20lower-order%20helped%20India%20post%20376%20in%20the%20first%20innings%2C%20the%20hosts%20swelled%20their%20lead%20to%20308%20by%20the%20end%20of%20play%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20day%20in%20which%2017%20wickets%20fell%2C%20India%20could%20add%20just%2037%20runs%20to%20their%20overnight%20total%20in%20the%20first%20hour%20against%20the%20second%20new%20ball%20as%20their%20first%20innings%20ended%20in%2091.2%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20reply%2C%20fast-bowling%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20picked%204%20for%2050%20in%20a%20relentless%20and%20searing%20bowling%20show%20to%20dismiss%20Bangladesh%20cheaply%20and%20help%20India%20take%20a%20227-run%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20does%20mostly%2C%20Bumrah%20was%20in%20just%20a%20different%20realm%20to%20be%20the%20standout%20bowler%20for%20India.%20Mohammed%20Siraj%2C%20Akash%20Deep%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20complemented%20him%20by%20keeping%20the%20pressure%20on%20to%20take%20two%20scalps%20each%20as%20Bangladesh%20crumbled%20in%20the%20face%20of%20baptism%20by%20fire%20from%20an%20exceptional%20Indian%20bowling%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20decided%20not%20to%20enforce%20follow-on%20and%20at%20stumps%2C%20reached%2081%2F3%20in%2023%20overs%20of%20their%20second%20inn