er%20at%20just%204%20or%205%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20done%20it%20since%20I%20was%20a%20kid%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20when%20we%20met%20in%20August.%20%26quot%3BI%20started%20going%20on%20my%20dad's%20boat%2C%20and%20my%205-year-old%20son%20just%20worked%20with%20us%20the%20day%20before%20yesterday%20for%20the%20first%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EKnowles%20learned%20many%20tricks%20of%20the%20trade%20from%20the%20lobstermen%20in%20his%20family.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224912%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Coastline%20of%20Schoodic%20Penninsula%20in%20Winter%20Harbor%2C%20Maine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eb209cce3009a0fac751ce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223684%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20coastline%20of%20the%20Schoodic%20Peninsula%20in%20Winter%20Harbor%2C%20Maine%2C%20where%20Knowles%20is%20based.%3Cp%3EJoshuaGoddard%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20generations%20of%20lobstermen%20in%20Knowles'%20family%20have%20fished%20in%20Winter%20Harbor%2C%20a%20small%20fishing%20village%20east%20of%20Bar%20Harbor.%20The%20generations%20before%20that%20were%20in%20a%20neighboring%20harbor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20things%20that%20I%20do%20on%20my%20boat%20are%20stuff%20that%20my%20grandfather%20learned%20how%20to%20do%20back%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20a%20way%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20things%20that%20I%20do%20are%20probably%20an%20older%20way%20of%20doing%20things%2C%20but%20I%20have%20an%20accumulative%20knowledge%20from%20my%20grandfather%2C%20great-grandfather%2C%20and%20my%20father.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20that%20knowledge%20has%20been%20passed%20down%20onto%20my%20boat%2C%20along%20with%20the%20locations%20where%20we%20fish%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20spots%20that%20my%20grandfather%20learned%2C%20I'm%20still%20fishing%20today.%20He%20always%20knew%20to%20get%20back%20there%20at%20a%20certain%20date%2C%20and%20then%20he'd%20tell%20my%20father%20to%20get%20back%20here%20at%20a%20certain%20date%2C%20and%20now%20my%20father%20told%20me%20to%20get%20back%20there%20at%20a%20certain%20date.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Knowles%20explained%20that%20a%20spot%20that%20was%20good%20one%20year%20may%20not%20be%20as%20good%20the%20next%2C%20or%20the%20year%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20definitely%20don't%20have%20it%20down%20to%20a%20science%20by%20any%20means%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnowles%20said%20that%20his%20mom%20would%20also%20go%20out%20with%20him%20on%20his%20boat%2C%20as%20well%20as%20his%20sisters%20%E2%80%94%20Knowles%20is%20actually%20a%20twin%2C%20and%20while%20his%20twin%20sister%20isn't%20a%20lobster%20fisherman%20herself%2C%20she%20is%20married%20to%20one%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnowles%20believes%20his%20generational%20knowledge%20has%20given%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bdifferent%20perspective%26quot%3B%20compared%20to%20someone%20who's%20newer%2C%20but%20that%20it's%20not%20considered%20better%20or%20worse%20to%20be%20a%20multigenerational%20lobsterman%20%E2%80%94%20just%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHe%20got%20his%20first%20skiff%20when%20he%20was%20around%2013%20years%20old%2C%20and%20he%20has%20been%20lobstering%20ever%20since.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222324%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lobster%20boats%20in%20Cape%20Porpoise%20harbor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eb2998ce3009a0fac76101%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221743%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELobster%20boats%20in%20Cape%20Porpoise%20harbor%20in%20Kennebunkport%2C%20Maine.%3Cp%3EGregory%20Rec%2FPortland%20Portland%20Press%20Herald%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20time%2C%20Knowles%20said%20he%20had%20around%20150%20traps%2C%20and%20it%20was%20more%20of%20a%20learning%20experience%20than%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20made%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20money%20also%2C%20but%20it%20was%20more%20for%20just%20the%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20when%20he%20turned%2015%20or%2016%2C%20he%20got%20a%20bigger%20boat%20and%20started%20working%20with%20his%20own%20crew.%20As%20a%20high%20school%20senior%2C%20he%20upgraded%20to%20a%20bigger%20boat%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20upgraded%20several%20times%20since%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20been%20doing%20it%20forever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EKnowles%20said%20that%20working%20as%20a%20lobsterman%20may%20be%20harder%20than%20people%20think.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225031%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20lobsterman%20hauls%20a%20lobster%20trap%20up%20onto%20the%20side%20of%20a%20boat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eb382dce3009a0fac770fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223773%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKnowles%20said%20that%20working%20on%20a%20lobster%20boat%20can%20be%20more%20physically%20demanding%20than%20people%20expect.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20profession's%20challenges%2C%20lobster%20licenses%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20come%20by%20in%20Maine.%20One%20way%20to%20procure%20one%20is%20to%20go%20through%20a%20student%20or%20apprenticeship%20program%2C%20which%20requires%20students%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20license%20before%20they%20turn%2023%20and%20to%20log%20at%20least%201%2C000%20hours%20working%20alongside%20a%20sponsor%20who%20holds%20a%20lobster%20license.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20older%20than%2023%20must%20join%20a%20waiting%20list%20for%20a%20license%2C%20but%20securing%20one%20can%20take%20years%20due%20to%20the%20state's%20limited%20entry%20system%20that%20restricts%20the%20number%20of%20fishermen%20who%20can%20hold%20commercial%20lobster%20licenses%20at%20any%20one%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20captains%2C%20if%20not%20all%20of%20them%2C%20started%20on%20the%20back%20of%20somebody's%20boat%20somewhere%2C%26quot%3B%20Knowles%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20an%20apprentice%20program%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20easy%20to%20get%20a%20license.%20It%20takes%20a%20long%20time.%20I've%20got%20friends%20that%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20get%20licenses%20for%2010%20years%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnowles%20added%20that%20the%20job%20is%20much%20more%20physical%20than%20one%20might%20think.%20Traps%20are%20heavy%2C%20and%20hauling%20them%20day%20in%20and%20day%20out%20can%20put%20stress%20on%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20brutal%20on%20the%20back%2C%20on%20the%20muscles%2C%20everything.%20It's%20hard%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20most%20dangerous%20part%20is%20getting%20wrapped%20up%20in%20that%20rope.%20That's%20how%20we%20lose%20the%20fishermen%20that%20we%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20despite%20the%20hard%20work%2C%20the%20career%20can%20be%20lucrative%20for%20some.%20Knowles%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bhighliners%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20top-producing%20lobstermen%2C%20can%20make%20around%20or%20over%20six%20figures%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20the%20career%20can%20be%20lucrative%20for%20some%20lobstermen%2C%20the%20fishing%20season%20is%20at%20its%20peak%20for%20only%20six%20months%20out%20of%20the%20year.%20While%20it's%20possible%20to%20fish%20for%20lobster%20year-round%2C%20and%20some%20lobstermen%20do%2C%20the%20main%20season%20lasts%20from%20June%20until%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EKnowles%20grew%20his%20social%20media%20following%20largely%20by%20sharing%20videos%20of%20egg-laden%20female%20lobsters%2C%20which%20are%20illegal%20to%20catch%20and%20keep.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20lobsterman%20holds%20a%20female%20lobster%20carrying%20eggs%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eb2650cfb7f307e572cff1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFemale%20lobsters%20that%20are%20able%20to%20carry%20eggs%20are%20illegal%20to%20catch%20and%20keep%20in%20Maine.%3Cp%3EJoe%20Raedle%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%20reported%20that%20a%20video%20Knowles%20posted%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40jacob__knowles%2Fvideo%2F6888376758949760261%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202020%20was%20one%20of%20his%20first%20to%20go%20viral.%20As%20of%20August%202024%2C%20it%20had%20roughly%206.2%20million%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2026-second%20clip%2C%20Knowles%20catches%20a%20female%20breeding%20lobster%20covered%20in%20eggs%20and%20explains%20that%20%26quot%3Blike%20on%20a%20farm%2C%20you%20wouldn't%20want%20to%20kill%20your%20breeders.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20he%20cuts%20a%20small%20notch%20in%20the%20lobster's%20tail%20before%20throwing%20it%20back%20into%20the%20ocean%2C%20a%20common%20practice%20with%20female%20breeding%20lobsters%20that%20has%20become%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flegislature.maine.gov%2Fstatutes%2F12%2Ftitle12sec6436.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emandated%20by%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20state.%20That%20way%2C%20any%20future%20lobstermen%20who%20catch%20a%20female%20lobster%20while%20she%20doesn't%20have%20any%20eggs%20will%20know%20that%20she's%20able%20to%20produce%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnowles%20called%20the%20rise%20in%20short-form%20content%2C%20like%20the%20videos%20he%20posts%20to%20Instagram%20and%20TikTok%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bpivotal%20moment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20world%20transformed%20from%20long-form%20videos%20to%20short-form%2C%20now%20the%20farmers%2C%20fishermen%2C%20hunters%2C%20anybody%20can%20pull%20out%20their%20cell%20phone%20and%20film%20a%2060-second%2C%2030-second%2C%2010-second%20clip%20and%20post%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnowles'%20videos%20now%20frequently%20surpass%205%20million%20views%2C%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40jacob__knowles%2Fvideo%2F7227933691547307306%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0from%202023%20has%20been%20viewed%20more%20than%2057%20million%20times.%20His%20success%20in%20catching%20viewers'%20attention%20has%20led%20to%20brand%20deals%2C%20which%20could%20mean%20even%20more%20income%20as%20a%20content%20creator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnowles%20said%20he%20and%20his%20team%20are%20still%20being%20choosey%20about%20who%20they%20work%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20being%20pretty%20selective%20on%20the%20brand%20deals%2C%20making%20sure%20they're%20authentic%20to%20the%20page%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20his%20videos%2C%20Knowles%20educates%20viewers%20on%20commonly%20asked%20questions%20about%20lobstering.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224965%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20male%20and%20female%20lobster%20side%20by%20side%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eb3899cfb7f307e572e3cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223724%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20male%20and%20female%20lobster%20positioned%20side%20by%20side.%20%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20explaining%20the%20telltale%20signs%20between%20male%20and%20female%20lobsters%20to%20showing%20how%20to%20remove%20barnacles%20from%20lobsters'%20shells%2C%20Knowles%20has%20created%20hundreds%20of%20videos%20showing%20the%20unique%20things%20he%20comes%20across%20as%20a%20lobsterman.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20first%2C%20it%20was%20just%20a%20hobby%20and%20fun%2C%26quot%3B%20Knowles%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20when%20I%20realized%20how%20much%20interest%20people%20had%20in%20it%2C%20I%20realized%20how%20much%20I%20enjoy%20teaching%20people%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGaining%20followers%20is%20one%20thing%2C%20but%20Knowles%20said%20that%20gaining%20respect%20as%20a%20lobsterman%20%E2%80%94%20and%20keeping%20it%20%E2%80%94%20has%20always%20been%20a%20priority%20for%20him.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jacob%20Knowles%20poses%20in%20front%20of%20Portland%20Harbor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eb3908cfb7f307e572e419%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221728%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJacob%20Knowles%20in%20front%20of%20Portland%20Harbor.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20he%20was%20concerned%20that%20his%20reputation%20among%20his%20fellow%20lobstermen%20would%20change%20after%20he%20potentially%20became%20known%20around%20town%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Instagram%20guy%2C%26quot%3B%20Knowles%20said%20that%20did%20cross%20his%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20concerned%20about%20that%20because%2C%20like%20I%20said%2C%20%5Bthis%20industry%20is%5D%20so%20respect-driven.%20And%20I'd%20spent%20my%20whole%20life%20building%20that%20respect%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20been%20cautious%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20page%20is%20done%20in%20a%20way%20that%20is%20looked%20up%20to%20and%20respected%20and%20shines%20a%20positive%20light%20on%20the%20industry%2C%20and%20the%20fishermen%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20can%20respect%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHe%20hopes%20to%20pass%20his%20knowledge%20down%20to%20his%20own%20son%2C%20should%20he%20choose%20to%20also%20pursue%20lobstering.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223179%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jacob%20Knowles%20and%20his%20son%20with%20a%20large%20lobster%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ec43aecfb7f307e57313a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222384%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJacob%20Knowles%20and%20his%20son%20with%20a%20large%20lo