e-anti-tobacco-spots-on-ott-124092100441_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20also%20proposed%20displaying%20anti-tobacco%20health%20warnings%20as%20prominent%20static%20messages%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20screen%20during%20the%20scenes%20that%20show%20use%20of%20tobacco%20products%20in%20all%20content%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fhealth-ministry-plans-mandatory-non-skippable-anti-tobacco-spots-on-ott-124092100441_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20A%20First%2C%20White%20House%20Engages%20With%20Pro-Khalistan%20Groups%2C%20Gives%20Assurance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20today%20met%20with%20a%20group%20of%20Sikhs%20who%20are%20sympathisers%20for%20the%20Khalistan%20movement%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20ever%20that%20they%20have%20officially%20engaged%20with%20such%20groups.%20The%20White%20House%20has%20also%20assured%20them%20%26quot%3Bprotection%20from%20any%20transnational%20aggression%20on%20its%20soil%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20said%20it%20is%20committed%20to%20%26quot%3Bprotecting%20American%20Citizens%26quot%3B%20from%20harm%20while%20they%20are%20within%20the%20borders%20of%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20development%20comes%20amid%20concerns%20that%20Canada%20and%20the%20US%20are%20giving%20shelter%20and%20asylum%20to%20Khalistani%20separatists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGroups%20aligned%20to%20the%20Khalistan%20separatist%20movement%20are%20banned%20in%20India%20and%20several%20of%20these%20organisations%20have%20carried%20out%20terrorist%20activities%20in%20the%20last%20few%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20US%20has%20not%20made%20any%20official%20comment%20on%20%26quot%3Bgiving%20shelter%26quot%3B%20to%20such%20elements%2C%20Canada%20had%20called%20it%20their%20%26quot%3Bfreedom%20of%20speech%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5C